1. Challenges with Non-Containerized Applications

traditional deployment mein kya dikkatein thi:

"Works on my machine"           — developer ke laptop pe chal raha tha, server pe nahi
Dependency hell                 — ek app ko Node 14 chahiye, dusri ko Node 18, dono same server pe nahi chal sakti
Environment mismatch            — Dev mein Ubuntu 20.04, Prod mein Ubuntu 18.04, library versions alag
Resource waste                  — har app ke liye alag VM banana padta tha, cost zyada
Slow scaling                    — nayi VM banana 10-15 minutes lagta tha



Containers yeh sab solve karte hain — ek image banao, kahi bhi chalao.
